data.description: Welcome to this well-maintained ranch home situated on 1.5 acres.  Located in Mattawan schools, this home is minutes from the main commercial area yet offers a private, picturesque setting.  The home features an open floor plan with a large dine in kitchen with coffee nook,, multiple sliding glass doors offering a great view of the fenced backyard as well as the very large composite deck.  The primary bedroom is very spacious and offers a primary bathroom ensuite.  The other 2 bedrooms are also very nice sized   Updates in the last 2 years include interior paint, carpet and refrigerator.  The lower level has a finished family room and large room for 4th bedroom with egress and offers loads of storage.  The home also has a carport, large 2 car detached garage, as well as a storage shed.
